snippet.title: The Oscars SUCK | Amber Heard Back For Aquaman 2? | WB Trolls Snyder Fans | Who's The Best Hulk?
snippet.description:
In this week's Geekly Wrap Up, we talk about the recent Oscars and discuss if the Oscars SUCK, WB trolling Snyder fans with the release of the 4k Josstice League, Amber Heard unfortunately returning for Aquaman 2,  Heath Ledger vs Joaquin Phoenix's Joker, Mark Ruffalo vs Edward Nortan's Hulk, Guy Gardner being cast in the Green Lantern tv show, and much more! #Oscars #AmberHeard #ZackSnydersJusticeLeague
